The interchangeable cooking surfaces allow you to cook either on a grate, or a griddle making this full service for just about any meal preparation. You can easily remove the grill from the stand and use it as a table top grill. With a cooking space of 285 square inches, and a 20,000 BTU output this is a great choice for those road trips requiring meals. The 2 burners are independently controlled, and have an instastart matchless lighting ignition system.Coleman Roadtrip LX Propane Grill
